Elbit Imaging Heads for Biggest Gain in 8 Months on Sale Report

-- B y   S h a r o n   W r o b e l
-- 
2011-07-04T12:19:54Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-04/elbit-imaging-heads-for-biggest-gain-in-8-months-on-sale-report.html
Elbit Imaging Ltd. (EMIT)  headed for the
biggest gain in more than eight months on a report the investor
in real estate and medical companies may sell off its share of a
planned residential project in  India .  The shares jumped 6.4 percent to 22.03 shekels at 2:46 p.m.
in Tel Aviv, heading for the biggest gain since Oct. 21. The
stock has declined 53 percent this year giving the Tel Aviv-
based company a market value of 561.2 million shekels ($165
million).  The company owns 80 percent of the property in Chennai and
is expected to receive about $250 million from the deal, the
financial newspaper  Globes reported , without saying where it got
the information.  To contact the reporter on this story:
{Sharon Wrobel} in  Tel Aviv  at 
